79
00:03:27,740 --> 00:03:28,875
Well, thanks, Robin.

80
00:03:28,875 --> 00:03:30,009
And welcome, everybody.

81
00:03:30,009 --> 00:03:30,910
Thanks for joining us.

82
00:03:30,910 --> 00:03:33,546
I'm personally extremely
excited that we're here today,

83
00:03:33,546 --> 00:03:36,349
celebrating the
launch of MIT HEALS.

84
00:03:36,349 --> 00:03:38,451
As you heard, I was
involved with Kris Prather

85
00:03:38,451 --> 00:03:39,919
in leading a faculty
committee that

86
00:03:39,919 --> 00:03:42,188
led to a series
of recommendations

87
00:03:42,188 --> 00:03:44,524
that arguably brought
