303
00:13:53,465 --> 00:13:56,001
size of the individual
who's being treated based

304
00:13:56,001 --> 00:13:58,604
on their height
and their weight.

305
00:13:58,604 --> 00:14:01,273
And by this very simple
formula, regardless

306
00:14:01,273 --> 00:14:04,577
of the particular
individual, whether they

307
00:14:04,577 --> 00:14:06,545
be very tall, short,
and heavy, they

308
00:14:06,545 --> 00:14:08,614
