very, very different.

311
00:14:12,751 --> 00:14:14,854
And their genetics is
likely to be very different.

312
00:14:14,854 --> 00:14:16,689
And their metabolism is
likely to be very different.

313
00:14:16,689 --> 00:14:19,191
But the formula doesn't pay
