505
00:24:05,110 --> 00:24:07,012
And what you see is
that it now stands

506
00:24:07,012 --> 00:24:11,183
alongside the physics-based and
the chemistry-based engineering

507
00:24:11,183 --> 00:24:12,050
disciplines.

508
00:24:12,050 --> 00:24:16,788
But now its science foundation
is molecular biology

509
00:24:16,788 --> 00:24:18,557
and genomic biology.

510
00:24:18,557 --> 00:24:22,527
And from that foundation,
