511
00:24:22,527 --> 00:24:25,897
in a predictively
designed way to apply

512
00:24:25,897 --> 00:24:30,135
to manufacturing, energy,
environment, defense,

513
00:24:30,135 --> 00:24:32,204
and medicine and health.

514
00:24:32,204 --> 00:24:36,041
So it's alongside those
in being able to address

515
00:24:36,041 --> 00:24:40,979
the challenges across the
