530
00:25:25,123 --> 00:25:28,793
and solely on the molecular
and genomic biology

531
00:25:28,793 --> 00:25:33,164
in an entirely new way that has
never existed at any institution

532
00:25:33,164 --> 00:25:34,199
worldwide.

533
00:25:34,199 --> 00:25:36,101
And now these
students are going on

534
00:25:36,101 --> 00:25:38,169
to become the next
generation who

535
00:25:38,169 --> 00:25:40,772
are addressing these
problems in ways

536
00:25:40,772 --> 00:25:43,074
that the physics-based
engineering

